>>630403316 (OP)
rightio:

> u = 3j
> v = 9i+2j
> u is parallel to the y axis since it has no i component.
> v is in the 1st quadrant of the coordinate system since both components are positive.
> thus the angle between them is equal to the angle between v and the y axis.
> making the vector a right angled triangle, we get acute angle = 90-arctan(9/2)
> = 88.6 deg
